ailyhadithonline\/2013\/09\/22\/muslim-defend-brother-honor\/","url_meta":{"origin":27003,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Honor: When a Muslim defends his brother&#8217;s reputation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever defends the reputation of his brother, Allah will defend his face from the Hellfire on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1931 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064e\u0651\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35393,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/03\/16\/abu-darda-sabr\/","url_meta":{"origin":27003,"position":2},"title":"Abu Darda on Patience: Be forbearing in the face of insults, curses","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Jubayr reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cGive up your reputation for the sake of Allah. Whoever abuses you, insults you, or fights you, leave him to Allah. If you do a bad deed, then ask forgiveness from Allah.\u201d Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq 47\/180\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":30966,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/24\/abu-darda-not-curse-anyone\/","url_meta":{"origin":27003,"position":3},"title":"Abu Darda on Curses: Do not curse anyone, not befitting believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Hakim ibn Jabir reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, was lying down between his companions and he had a cloth over his face. A priest passed by him and they were amazed at how fat he was. They said, \u201cO Allah, curse him! How big is he!\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3751,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/23\/abu-darda-hate-his-sinful-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":27003,"position":4},"title":"Abu Darda on Sinners: Hate his sinful deeds, do not abuse him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qilaba reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, passed by\u00a0a man who was being beaten because of his sin and they were cursing\u00a0him. Abu Darda\u00a0said, \u201cWhat do you think if he had fallen into a well. Would you not try to rescue him?\u201d They said yes.\u00a0Abu Darda\u00a0said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37343,"url":"htt